nd even the Galaxy or else it's Gameover!<br><br></li><li>Traverse 8 different stages in the Story Mode, including the skies of a city or the vast space.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/972050/extras/b1c4d208bb2df4fc975c304ca7eba2ec.poster.avif?t=1677273792\" width=232 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/972050/extras/b1c4d208bb2df4fc975c304ca7eba2ec.webm?t=1677273792\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/972050/extras/b1c4d208bb2df4fc975c304ca7eba2ec.mp4?t=1677273792\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li>Fight over 20 kind of aliens, including 4 evil bosses.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/972050/extras/2013a31c13bb0d9ef6974d83c044f469.poster.avif?t=1677273792\" width=232 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/972050/extras/2013a31c13bb0d9ef6974d83c044f469.webm?t=1677273792\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/972050/extras/2013a31c13bb0d9ef6974d83c044f469.mp4?t=1677273792\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li>Secret unlockables that further develop the story and add more gameplay!<br><br></li><li>A Super Heroic original soundtrack full of electronic beats!</li></ul>",
